rows.label: qst650331_msg0002
rows.name:
Friends know how hard it is to track
down world-traveling adventurers?

rows.label: qst650331_msg0003
rows.name:
Kedokedo is seasoned veteran courier,
but find friends take every ounce
of resolve and determination.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0004
rows.name:
Eventually, Kedokedo decide
to wait for adventurers
to come to Kedokedo.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0005
rows.name:
It unconventional delivery technique but
seems to be pay off. Oh! Package. This
is for friends from Iyasaki Village.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0006
rows.name:
Is from Correl, but she got
from kid named Kazuna.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0007
rows.name: Kazuna got from kid named Martis.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0009
rows.name:
...Anyway, it very valuable Core
Crystal, so everybody say to Kedokedo
"Please to not drop or break".

rows.label: qst650331_msg0010
rows.name:
Villagers find it in dusty box in
attic, and decide must entrust to
people who use it in good way.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0011
rows.name:
That why they give to Kedokedo.
Kedokedo just have trustworthy
face, me guess.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0012
rows.name: And now Kedokedo entrust to you.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0013
rows.name:
It very valuable, hence innovative new
courier style of Kedokedo involving no
movement and no risk of lose or break.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0015
rows.name:
Such out-of-box thinking is proof
that Kedokedo leveled up as courier.

rows.label: qst650331_msg0016
rows.name:
Maybe brother Dokedoke interested
in learnings of Kedokedo...

rows.label: qst650331_msg0017
rows.name:
Please not to forget rate at
least four and half stars!
